node.text:
THROWBACK to me and @natalybiskay working at our Villa in Thailand. Do you remember freely traveling to other countries? I do. 😢 Seriously this villa was awesome and the views are insane but the cook there made the best chicken pad thai I’d ever had. Holy shit 😂 

P.S. Have you ever thought about Passive Income? My team and I are looking for a few more ppl who want to earn a full-time passive income from home using AirBNB without owning property. If you’re interested, message me the word “Air bnb”. Thanks

node.text:
WATCH THIS: At my dad’s last birthday, we had t-shirts made of him! Now think about how meta this is: My dad is in this photo. And in this photo, my dad is wearing a shirt of a photo where my dad was in that photo. This feels like the start of a Rick and Morty episode. Throw some Mr. Nimbus in there and I’m watching. 

P.S. Have you ever thought about Passive Income? My team and I are looking for a few more ppl who want to earn a full-time passive income from home using AirBNB without owning property. If you’re interested, message me the word “Travel”. Thanks!
